<section class="section is-medium">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="title has-text-centered is-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="content">
          <h3>What is a landing page?</h3>
          <p>
            A landing page is a simple website that is displayed when someone visits your domain.
            They help capture inbound traffic.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="content">
          <h3>How are offers verified?</h3>
          <p>
            Firstly, users cannot submit any offers that are below your domain's minimum asking price.
            Secondly, all users must confirm their offers by email. Offers that are not confirmed
            will not be sent to you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="content">
          <h3>What kind of analytics are provided?</h3>
          <p>
            We track stats like how many views your domain gets, where your visitors come from, how they get
            to your domains, and much more!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="content">
          <h3>What payment options does DomaHub accept?</h3>
          <p>
            We accept payments from all major credit and debit cards in more than 130 currencies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="content">
          <h3>How do I get paid?</h3>
          <p>
            You must link a bank account with DomaHub. Once a transaction has been confirmed, we will deposit the money directly into your account
            once it has been processed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="content">
          <h3>Can I cancel my Premium subscription?</h3>
          <p>
            You can cancel your Premium subscription at any time. Your account will still remain active and your Premium status will last
            until the end of the current billing cycle (1 month).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content has-text-centered">
      <p>
        Have other questions? Visit our <a tabindex="0" class="is-underlined is-primary" href="/faq">FAQ</a>!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

